Body:
Description: The DLP is synced to an Active Directory and the very first time it sinced it imported the Admins we have in the designated groups of Admins and they show as Ad imported since they hay "AD" as a User Type in the System Administrator section. 
After such, we added some more people to the AD Admin Group within our Active Directory and click on "System Settings - Active Directory Authentication - Syn AD Administrator" which shows a  message saying "AD administrators have been synchronized!" but the admins do not show up in the "System Administrators" section
Next Steps Updated: A remote session was scheduled in order to investigate.
What We've Learned Updated: The customer is facing issues when they try to import the AD admins.
Invitation updated. Attendees: Emil Podar, Jonatan Pregliasco
